title: Overview
description: If you have both [Data Export](/docs/integrations/data-export) and [Experimentation](/docs/home/experimentation) enabled for your LaunchDarkly account, you should have access to Snowflake native Experimentation. If you do not have access or need help getting started, contact your LaunchDarkly representative or [start a Support ticket](https://support.launchdarkly.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
